node.text: Couldn't have said it better myself 🙌 all jobs are essential to keep society going
haha this survey got everyone on fire 🔥

IS YOUR JOB REALLY NON-ESSENTIAL?🤔
In the now-famous infographic in Singapore, the top 5 non-essential jobs are listed as: 1.Artist 2. Telemarketer 3. Social Media Manager/PR Specialist 4.Business Consultant 5.HR Manager

While these occupations may not be ‘essential’ for survival, they are very essential for sanity, aesthetics, culture, positivity, the economy, customer experience and MORE. 🙏

Though while we’re at it. Even though we may have stopped the clapping and singing, lots of love to our healthcare heroes, and the ones providing care and maintaining order here and the world over. ❤️
@whytrywhat I know right! I was like whaaaaaaaaat. But I suppose some aspect of smaller picture thinking comes into play here.
I saw this too and was so mad!!!
True! It is a really important job
@loislusotan yes! The arts are so important to mental health!
Everyone plays a role in society. We are doing our best in our unique ways to care for each other. Let's give ”non-essential workers” some credits 💪 Artist stands for artist.
@ricky_menon especially now right. Essential just has so many contexts.
Any job that puts food on your table is essential.
Couldn't have said it better myself 🙌 all jobs are essential to keep society going
haha this survey got everyone on fire 🔥
